snippet.title: JumpStart 2nd Grade Math/Math for Second Graders
snippet.description: The evil Ratso has taken over the kingdom and imprisoned the royal family in the mirror! It is up to brave knight CJ Frog and his sidekick Edison Firefly to free the royal family, rack up enough bravery points to defeat Ratso and save the kingdom!
